reviewText: Case and cassette in great condition as seller said. My grand daughter loves this movie as her mom did 25 yrs ago. Very happy with my purchase.
This was a favored show from my childhood that i wanted to make sure i had for when i have children.

This is one of the cheesiest cartoons I have ever seen. However, I am a teacher at a Daycare, and this is the only movie that sedates and engages the little kids AND the big kids. I don't know what it is; it may be the colors, the candy park, or the brightly colored animals. Whatever it is, it works wonders!
